  "title": "Unable to minify instantsearch.js using YUI compressor",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for participating in this project! We will try to answer as soon as possible 🙏\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug 🐛**\r\nYUI compressor gives error when minifying instantsearch.js. This is the uncompressed file available in dist folder which we are referring to.\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce 🔍**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. Go to https://www.piliapp.com/minify/yui-compressor/\r\n2. Copy and paste instantsearch.js code in the text field\r\n3. Click compress\r\n4. Minification fails\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior 💭**\r\nThe code should minify.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nWe use Adobe Experience Manager which uses YUI compressor. Our workflow requires us to use unminified versions of JS files as minification is directly done by AEM server. Using unminified version also doesn't work as minification is enabled at the server.",
